        <h1 class="greeting">Hi, there!</h1>
        <p class="intro-text">
            I'm <strong>Shradha Lakshman</strong>, a dental hygiene student at UBC passionate about 
            <strong>health education and innovation</strong>.
        </p>
        <p class="intro-text">
            I'm the founder and CEO of Eureka Enterprises, where I'm developing Eureka: 
            QuestScapes - a gamified web-based application for HIV/AIDS education among 
            Canadian youth. I've had the privilege of representing the dental hygiene 
            profession and UBC Faculty of Dentistry across Northern BC through the 
            Healthcare Travelling Roadshow, and held a position as Collaborative Health 
            Education Project Assistant, advancing accessibility-driven curriculum redesign at 
            one of the top health institutions in the world.
        </p>

