                    <h3 class="featured-title">Eureka: QuestScapes</h3>
                    <p class="featured-subtitle">Gamified Health Initiative</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h4 class="project-title">Gamified HIV/AIDS Education for Youth</h4>
                    <p class="project-description">
                        As founder and CEO of Eureka Enterprises, I am leading the development of Eureka: QuestScapes — a pioneering, gamified web-based platform transforming HIV/AIDS education for Canadian youth. This forward-thinking initiative received an $800 bursary from North American non-profit LetsStopAIDS, acknowledging its innovative impact and groundbreaking approach to health education. By utilizing interactive storytelling, immersive gameplay, and engaging trivia-based combat mechanics within a classic 2D platformer, Eureka enables youth to build health literacy, confront stigma, and embrace preventive behaviors.
                    </p>
                    <span class="coming-soon">WEBSITE COMING SOON</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
