                    <span class="tag-community">Community Education</span>
                </div>
                <div class="card-header northcoast-header">
                    <h3 class="featured-title">North Coast</h3>
                    <p class="featured-subtitle">Travelling Healthcare Roadshow</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h4 class="project-title">Inspiring Future Health Professionals</h4>
                    <p class="project-description">
                        As the Dental Hygiene Representative for UNBC's 2025 Healthcare Travelling Roadshow, I delivered dynamic oral health education across Northern BC's North Coast, representing the dental hygiene profession and UBC Faculty of Dentistry. Through interactive workshops with students in grades 4–12, I underscored the significance of the oral-systemic link and emphasized dental hygiene's critical role as a primary care profession within the health sector. By collaborating with educators and community leaders, I tailored content to engage and empower participants, fostering curiosity and confidence.
                    </p>
                    <a href="https://www.terracestandard.com/local-news/students-urged-to-consider-health-careers-7987947" target="_blank" class="project-link">READ FEATURE ARTICLE</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="featured-card">
                <div class="section-header" style="margin-bottom: 0; padding: 1.5rem 2.5rem 1rem 2.5rem;">
